title: Jerry Jones, less is more, Aaron Rodgers-Russell Wilson, & the Blazing 5
itunes:title: Jerry Jones, less is more, Aaron Rodgers-Russell Wilson, & the Blazing 5
description:
Colin discusses Cowboys owner Jerry Jones' latest comments and what might happen if they lose to the Bills, why he doesn't want more teams in the NCAAFB Playoff, why he thinks Russell Wilson is now better than Aaron Rodgers, and his new Blazing 5 picks for the week. Guests include Nick Wright, Greg Cosell, Joel Klatt, Bucky Brooks, and Jason McIntyre.
